mainsentences.text: I am looking into purchasing the new model HB12S pizza oven from your Pizza Technologies website but not sure which will be best for what I will use it for.
Thank you so much for your help and I look forward to hearing about your portable pizza ovens!
I want it to be able to fit a 16-inch pizza but most likely nothing bigger.

logic.value: the new model HB12S pizza oven
